TI  - Conditional Prediction and Unbiasedness in Structural Equations
AU  - Kaufman, Gordon M.
AB  - [The usual least squares estimator of a set of reduced form parameters is unbiased. We show here that a certain conditional least squares estimator is also unbiased, and record some related distribution theory.]
